item.description:
Hi Fellow Qi Cultivators,

Since there are a number of new members who are relatively new to Qigong, I'll be going over some of the basics of the Daoist Qigong I practice and review some of the Qigong we did last month with my teacher, Master Yuanming Zhang. This may include Feng Shui (Wind Water) Qigong, gathering universal Qi and moving it through the 3 dantian (literally "elixir field"), the energy centers we use in Qigong.

I'm also open to requests or other ideas. Just let me know.

Dee
item.how_to_find_us: The Louise Mastrangelo Room is on the second floor.
